  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Courtyard offers a peaceful stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d}" title="Hakuba">Hakuba</a>. Just a few minutes’ walk from the main streets of Echo Land this hotel acts as a great retreat after exploring the great powder on offer. The free bus shuttle directly outside the hotel offers efficient transportation to the lifts at Happo One, Goryu and Hakuba 47. Breakfast at the Courtyard is a delight with various continental options, eggs to order and a selection of Japanese foods to try. </p>
